These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, pomegranate, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, hiking, writing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, vegafina, dannemann, bongani
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, february, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, lacrosse, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
 1. the person eating broccoli is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 2. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the vegafina-smoker is between the person driving the bus and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is the bluemaster-smoker##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating cabbage##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite     | hot-chocolate | fanta      |
| Food          | pomegranate | cabbage    | broccoli      | raspberry  |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | writing    | camping       | hiking     |
| Cigar   | dannemann        | bongani       | vegafina          | bluemaster |
| Birthday           | february    | july | november      | may     |
| Sport         | badminton   | baseball   | lacrosse      | sailing    |
| Transport     | bike        | bus        | snowmobile    | jet-ski    |

