House: colonial, craftsman, ranch-style, cape-cod
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, horse, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, snowboarding, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, roller, trike
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the colonial house##1
 3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the craftsman house is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the fan of hip-hop##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the fan of blues is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person eating blueberry is between the person driving the roller and the person eating cucumber##2
13. the ranch-style house is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |       4       |
